Standards-Version: 3.9.1
Homepage: http://games.aleva.com.br/jwltief

Package: jwltief
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, jwltief-data (= ${source:Version})
Description: Play a thief and collect jewels
 Jwltef is a game where you control a
 thief with the mouse and aim to collect
 as many jewels as possible, dodging
 moving enemies.

Package: jwltief-data
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ttf-jwltief (= ${source:Version})
Description: Play a thief and collect jewels (data package)
 Jwltef is a game where you control a
 thief with the mouse and aim to collect
 as many jewels as possible, dodging
 moving enemies.
 .
 (This package contains the data files.)

Package: ttf-jwltief
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Play a thief and collect jewels (font package)
 Jwltef is a game where you control a
 thief with the mouse and aim to collect
 as many jewels as possible, dodging
 moving enemies.
 .
 (This package contains the font files.)
